              },
              "free_text": [
                " The total error in each cross section was",
                "obtained by combining the following individual errors",
                "in quadrature:",
                "  * The error in the alpha-beam flux was around 4-7%.",
                "  * The efficiency of the gamma detector was known with",
                "    in an uncertainty of 3-5%.",
                "  * The error in the initial count rate at the end of",
                "    the irradiation as determined by the least",
                "    squares fitting procedure was about 0.5-2.5%.",
                "  * The error in the decay data used was <1%",
                "  * the error in the target thickness was 0.5-1.5%."
              ]
            }
